      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 465,
      "message": "Introducing a new tag ncmp-dmi-plugin-csit specifically for the CSITs which will be used in the test.properties file to pull the latest dmi image(which will have changes from the latest commit). \nI am not using <tag>${project.version}-latest</tag> as project.version is dynamic and we dont have it accessible in setup script.\n\nI want your opinion if I can use one of the below tags.\n1. ncmp-dmi-plugin-csit [present in commit ${project.name}-csit ]\n2. latest\n3. some other suggestion ??",
